snippet.title: Reasoning AVG game 《The Vigilant Villa》 Demo has launched on Steam now！
snippet.description:
《The Vigilant Villa》 has launched the demo on Steam！ Come to experience it ！ https://store.steampowered.com/app/1254900/The_Vigilant_Villa/ 
 Closed circle of suspects storyline，full with conspiracy and suspicion,who can escape here alive ?
Multiple puzzles,all mystery clues,looking for the marks murderer has left in the darkness.
